                "description": {
                  "paragraph": [
                    "Start the day off with a rush of energy with these Dunkin' Original Blend coffee pods. The medium roast provides a balanced flavor that's smooth yet bold, while the individual pods let you make a single serving at a time. With 22 pods in each pack, this Keurig K-Cup Dunkin' coffee is ideal for stocking up your home or workplace. The great tasting flavors and roasts from Dunkin'\u00ae are now available in convenient Keurig\u00ae K-Cup\u00ae pods. The same delicious coffee served in Dunkin'\u00ae restaurants is now available for your office with the same consistent taste and recipe used for over 60 years."
                  ],
                  "descriptionLineSize": 2,
                  "bullets": [
                    "Coffee K-Cups for Keurig brewers",
                    "Medium-roast coffee with Original Blend flavor",
                    "22 K-Cups per box",
                    "Orthodox Union Kosher",
                    "Made with 100% Arabica coffee"
                  ],
                  "headliner": [
                    "Enjoy a rich, smooth beverage that helps wake you up with this 22-pack of Keurig K-Cup Dunkin' original coffee pods."
                  ],
                  "expandedDescr": [
